sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 学生
    participant API as 🔌 FastAPI
    participant Sup as 🧭 Supervisor
    participant Planner as 📋 Planner Agent
    participant TR as 📖 text_retrieval
    participant KR as 🕸️ kg_retrieval
    participant PK as 🤖 parallel_knowledge
    participant Synth as 🔀 Synthesis Agent
    participant Gov as 🛡️ Governance
    participant Refl as 💭 Reflection
    participant KB as 📚 知识库+KG

    Note over User,KB: ===== 场景A: 简单概念查询 (快路径) =====
    User->>API: "什么是进程死锁？"
    API->>Sup: route_question()
    Sup->>Sup: classify → AdaptiveDepth=standard → 不触发Planner
    Sup->>PK: 直连 knowledge_agent
    PK->>KB: knowledge_search (文本+KG)
    KB-->>PK: FusedEvidence + 结构化KG证据
    PK->>Gov: 前置守卫: 检索调用检测 ✅
    Gov->>Gov: 后置治理: 来源检查/伪造检测
    Gov->>Refl: Reflection: 证据充分性评估
    Refl-->>API: 最终答案 + 来源引用
    API-->>User: Markdown格式回答

    Note over User,KB: ===== 场景B: 跨学科对比查询 (复杂路径) =====
    User->>API: "虚拟存储器和Cache的异同点是什么？"
    API->>Sup: route_question()
    Sup->>Sup: classify → comparison+long → AdaptiveDepth=deep → use_planner=True
    Sup->>Planner: 路由到 planner_node
    Planner->>KB: LLM查询分解
    KB-->>Planner: ExecutionPlan {3 subtasks}
    Note over Planner: t1: "虚拟存储器原理" → text_retrieval<br/>t2: "Cache映射方式" → text_retrieval<br/>t3: "两者异同对比" → knowledge_agent

    par Send fan-out (LangGraph并行分发)
        Planner->>TR: Send(t1)
        TR->>KB: text_search (纯文本)
        KB-->>TR: TextEvidence[]
    and
        Planner->>TR: Send(t2)
        TR->>KB: text_search (纯文本)
        KB-->>TR: TextEvidence[]
    and
        Planner->>KR: Send(t3)
        KR->>KB: kg_search (纯KG)
        KB-->>KR: KGEvidence{nodes, edges, paths}
    end

    Note over Synth: operator.add reducer 自动累积 agent_outputs
    TR-->>Synth: agent_output[0]
    TR-->>Synth: agent_output[1]
    KR-->>Synth: agent_output[2]

    Synth->>Synth: _deduplicate_outputs() 去重
    Synth->>KB: LLM合并 (synthesis_strategy=compare)
    KB-->>Synth: 合并后答案 + 矛盾标注 + 来源归属
    Synth->>Gov: govern_answer()
    Gov->>Refl: reflect()
    Refl-->>API: 最终对比分析答案
    API-->>User: Markdown对比表格 + 来源引用
